Class ProductCarPaymentVoucher

public class ProductCarPaymentVoucher

    Details of voucher information indicating prepayment.

        Details of voucher information indicating prepayment.

        Parameters:
        type - Indicates what part of the amount the Voucher covers. (e.g. Full credit, partial credit)
        amount - Indicates the amount covered in case of partial credit voucher.
        currency - Indicates the currency in case of partial credit voucher.
        decimalPlace - Indicates the decimal place in case of partial credit voucher.
        billingNumber - Reference number of the Billing Account that will be charged for the payment.
        providerReference - Unique Identifier created by the Car rental provider to identify this voucher.
